### Grid

A CSS grid container. Uses triple-colon.

```
:::grid[3|16px]{
::card[Card 1]{Content}
||
::card[Card 2]{Content}
||
::card[Card 3]{Content}
}
```

- **`[cols|gap]`** — number of columns (or CSS `grid-template-columns` value) and gap size
- **`{cell0||cell1||…}`** — one segment per cell

#### Preview

